<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">梅雀图 23cm×24cm 伪作</span></p>
<p><img width="677px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190302/1ba34764c727400c9b295e2ba29b88a7.jpeg" /></p>
<p><img width="677px" src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190302/0322d246931d466eb44aa9c35d454065.jpeg" /></p>
